    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 50-53.</p><p>Legendary Points</p><p>Starting at 20th level, you gain Legendary Points. Your level determines the number of points you have, as shown in the Legendary Points column of the Legendary Monk table. You can take the Recover action on your turn to regain all expended Legendary Points. You can spend these points to fuel various features.</p></div>",
